---
// Coverage Section - Cobertura de servicio - Tailwind + CSS personalizado
---

<section id="cobertura" class="py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24 xl:py-28 bg-bg-cream relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Logo watermark -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.035] z-0">
    <img src="/logo/logo2.svg" alt="" class="w-[600px] h-[600px] lg:w-[800px] lg:h-[800px] object-contain" />
  </div>
  
  <!-- Patrón de fondo industrial - CSS personalizado -->
  <div class="coverage-pattern"></div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-10 xl:px-12 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
    
    <!-- Header - Tailwind text utilities -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 md:mb-16 lg:mb-20 animate-on-scroll">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); letter-spacing: 0.02em;" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-normal text-primary mb-4 md:mb-5 lg:mb-6 leading-none uppercase">
        Cobertura de Servicio
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-secondary/80 leading-relaxed font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Brindamos nuestros servicios en sitio, desplazándonos directamente a su planta industrial 
        para minimizar tiempos de inactividad y garantizar la continuidad de su operación.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Grid de cobertura - Tailwind responsive -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14 xl:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Tarjeta de información - Tailwind + CSS personalizado -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="coverage-card">
          <div class="coverage-card-icon">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-display); letter-spacing: 0.02em;" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-normal text-primary mb-5 lg:mb-6 text-center lg:text-left leading-none uppercase">
            Servicio en Toda la Región
          </h3>
          
          <p style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-secondary/90 text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed font-light mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-center lg:text-left max-w-2xl">
            Nuestro equipo técnico se desplaza a su ubicación para realizar 
            todos los servicios de reparación y mantenimiento directamente en su planta, 
            ahorrándole tiempo y costos de transporte de equipos.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Lista de beneficios - Tailwind spacing -->
          <ul class="space-y-2.5 md:space-y-3">
            <li class="coverage-benefit">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Atención en su planta industrial</span>
            </li>
            <li class="coverage-benefit">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Sin costos de transporte de equipos</span>
            </li>
            <li class="coverage-benefit">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Menor tiempo de inactividad</span>
            </li>
            <li class="coverage-benefit">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Diagnóstico in situ inmediato</span>
            </li>
            <li class="coverage-benefit">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Servicio de emergencia disponible</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Imagen ilustrativa - Tailwind utilities -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-200">
        <div class="coverage-image-wrapper">
          <img 
            src="/imagenes/imagen6.webp" 
            alt="Cobertura de servicio en planta industrial" 
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          
          <!-- Stats flotantes - CSS personalizado -->
          <div class="coverage-stat coverage-stat-1">
            <div class="coverage-stat-icon">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">24/7</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-200">Disponibilidad</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="coverage-stat coverage-stat-2">
            <div class="coverage-stat-icon">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2h</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-200">Tiempo Respuesta</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- CTA para contacto - Tailwind utilities -->
    <div class="mt-12 md:mt-16 lg:mt-20 text-center animate-on-scroll">
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-lg md:text-xl text-secondary/90 mb-5 md:mb-6 font-light">
        ¿Su planta está fuera del área habitual? <span class="font-semibold text-primary">Consúltenos</span>
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/contacto" 
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary text-white font-semibold px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-steel transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 text-sm md:text-base"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
        </svg>
        Consultar Disponibilidad
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Patrón de fondo industrial - CSS personalizado */
  .coverage-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: 
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 30px,
        rgba(49, 61, 73, 0.03) 30px,
        rgba(49, 61, 73, 0.03) 31px
      ),
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 30px,
        rgba(49, 61, 73, 0.03) 30px,
        rgba(49, 61, 73, 0.03) 31px
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  /* Tarjeta de cobertura - CSS personalizado */
  .coverage-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .coverage-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
  
  .coverage-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 5px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-rust), var(--color-primary));
  }
  
  .coverage-card-icon {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-steel));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(49, 61, 73, 0.2);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .coverage-card-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
  
  /* Beneficios lista - CSS personalizado */
  .coverage-benefit {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  
  .coverage-benefit svg {
    color: var(--color-rust);
  }
  
  /* Imagen con stats flotantes - CSS personalizado */
  .coverage-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .coverage-stat {
    position: absolute;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-steel));
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(49, 61, 73, 0.3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .coverage-stat-1 {
    top: 2rem;
    right: -1rem;
  }
  
  .coverage-stat-2 {
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: -1rem;
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
  }
  
  .coverage-stat-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .coverage-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .coverage-stat {
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 280px;
      position: static;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
